title: Sidewall, 1905–15
inscribed: Printed in right selvedge: "CONOWINGO.W.P.Co." Pattern No. "712"
description:
Scrolling foliage with beading and acanthus leaves. Ground is pink. Embossed paper with small flowers and scroll motif. Printed in pinks and metallic gold.
